node.text: Awe summer nights, I love you!! Nothing beats longer days and warm nights. Why does it go by so fast!! We recently added a new @eufyofficial wireless security camera to our home! We already have Eufy cameras and I can’t recommend them enough! We added the eufy SoloCam E40. It’s wireless, has 120 day battery life, two audio and free storage!  You can see everything that is happening at your home. I love having cameras when we go on vacation, because I can see what the dogs are doing, when packages arrive and who is showing up at our house! The picture quality is so clear too. I always say, in this day in age why wouldn’t you have security cameras! They’re wireless and so easy to install! They give you so much peace of mind too.
